title: How I Scored The Dream Home
itunes:title: How I Scored The Dream Home
description:
Zach has been crystal clear about his goals and has reverse engineered them down to a solid plan of action. His dream house has been on his vision board for years, and he thought he still had years to go, but Zach has smashed that goal.  Coming to you live from his dream house for the first time, Zach shares how to make your own dreams a reality. 

The dream home wasn’t the only goal Zach has realized lately. The very first annual Alpha Underdog event is scheduled for July 15th.  With a variety of guest speakers, guests will learn how to scale their business working only 16 hours a week, and more importantly, feel fulfilled doing it.  Upgrading to a larger venue, there’s still space left, and it’s something you won’t want to miss.

 

What You’ll Learn:

  • How to reverse engineer your goals.
  • Why you shouldn’t fear a recession. 
  • Who will be speaking at the Alpha Underdog event.
  • And much more!!

 

Favorite Quote:

“In the past, I’ve been really bad at this, but we’re about to celebrate this time.” 

- Zach Babcock

 

Connect with Zach:

LinkedIn

Instagram

How to Get Involved:

Get podcasting help here.

For more on how to grow your business, check out this episode. 


If you enjoyed this episode, head over and visit us on Apple Podcasts - leave a review and let us know what you thought! Your feedback keeps us going. Thanks for helping us spread the word!
